{%- comment -%}
  LIFETIME — Quiz v2 Result-Page

  Parameter (vom Section-Aufruf):
    hero_female  → Bild-URL bei state.gender === 'female'
    hero_male    → Bild-URL bei state.gender === 'male' oder 'diverse' (Fallback)
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign _hero_female = hero_female | default: 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2173/8340/files/lifetime-sport-mood-tennis-woman.png?v=1777040629' -%}
{%- assign _hero_male = hero_male | default: 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2173/8340/files/lifetime-lifestyle-2_800x800.png?v=1777898071' -%}
{%- assign _cta_image = cta_image | default: 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2173/8340/files/product-8585364.png?v=1768563330' -%}
{%- assign _cta_image_bonus = cta_image_bonus | default: 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0621/2173/8340/files/33eea4ca-2b8c-40f6-8a00-abced1d6c5b2-1762948710197.png?v=1762948715' -%}

<div class="lt-quiz-result" data-quiz-result>

  {%- comment -%} 0 — Hero-Bild (gender-personalisiert, JS swap) ───── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="lt-quiz-result__hero">
    <img
      src="{{ _hero_male }}"
      data-result-hero
      data-hero-female="{{ _hero_female }}"
      data-hero-male="{{ _hero_male }}"
      alt=""
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
    >
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} 1 — Hook: die drei Topics ALS Headline ──────────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lt-quiz-result__header">
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__kicker">Dein Ergebnis</p>
    <h2 class="lt-quiz-result__h1" data-result-h1>Hier ist dein Bild.</h2>
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__sub" data-result-sub></p>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} 1b — Bio-Age-Schätzung (Pass | Biologisch ▲/▼) ────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lt-quiz-result__bioage" data-result-bioage>
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-label">Dein geschätztes biologisches Alter</p>
    <div class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-numbers">
      <div class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-side">
        <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-side-label">Pass</span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-num" data-bioage-pass>—</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-side lt-quiz-result__bioage-side--bio">
        <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-side-label">Biologisch</span>
        <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-num" data-bioage-num>—</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Ruhige Delta-Skala: Pass = Mitte (50%), Bio-Marker gleitet per JS auf Zielposition, Lücke getönt {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale-fill" data-bioage-scale-fill></span>
      <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale-dot lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale-dot--pass"></span>
      <span class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale-dot lt-quiz-result__bioage-scale-dot--bio" data-bioage-scale-bio></span>
    </div>

    <p class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-delta" data-bioage-delta></p>
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__bioage-disclaimer">
      Schätzung aus deinem Lebensstil. Der echte Test misst dein epigenetisches Alter über 10 CpG-Methylierungs-Marker.
    </p>

    {%- comment -%} P2 — Kauf-CTA direkt in die Bio-Alter-Karte integriert (dark teal) {%- endcomment -%}
    <a
      class="lt-quiz-result__cta-primary lt-quiz-result__bioage-cta"
      href="/products/lifetime-age-dna?utm_source=quiz&amp;utm_medium=result-page&amp;utm_campaign=cta-early"
      data-result-pdp-cta
    >
      Zum AGE&amp;DNA-Test · 349&nbsp;€
    </a>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} 2 — Depth: die drei Themen ausgepackt ───────────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lt-quiz-result__themes-section">
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__themes-lead">Was deine Gene dazu verraten.</p>
    <h3 class="lt-quiz-result__h2">Deine drei wichtigsten Themen im Detail.</h3>
    <div class="lt-quiz-result__themes" data-result-themes>
      {%- comment -%} JS rendert 3 <article>-Blöcke {%- endcomment -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} 3 — Breadth: was der Test sonst noch zeigt ───────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lt-quiz-result__scope">
    <h3 class="lt-quiz-result__h2">Plus alles, was dein Test sonst zeigt.</h3>
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__scope-sub">
      <strong>187 Reports</strong> zu 22 DNA-Bereichen plus dein epigenetisches Profil. Markiert sind die direkt zu deinen Themen gehörigen. Die anderen entdeckst du beim Auspacken.
    </p>
    <ul class="lt-quiz-result__pills" data-result-scope-pills>
      {%- assign cats = 'gesunde-alterung|Gesunde Alterung,supplements|Supplements,vitamine|Vitamine,sensitivitaeten|Sensitivitäten,stoffwechsel|Stoffwechsel,fitness|Fitness,verletzung-regeneration|Verletzung & Regeneration,mental-health|Mental Health,psychologisch|Psychologisch,schlaf|Schlaf,stress|Stress,herz|Herz,atemwege|Atemwege,augen|Augen,haare|Haare,niere|Niere' | split: ',' -%}
      {%- for c in cats -%}
        {%- assign parts = c | split: '|' -%}
        <li class="lt-quiz-result__pill" data-scope-cat="{{ parts[0] }}">{{ parts[1] }}</li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
    <p class="lt-quiz-result__scope-epi">
      Plus deine epigenetischen Marker: <strong>Biologisches Alter</strong> · <strong>Entzündung</strong>
    </p>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} 4 — CTA (dunkle Card, Code per E-Mail Framing) ────── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lt-quiz-result__cta-section">
    <div class="lt-quiz-result__cta-card">
      <div class="lt-quiz-result__cta-media" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="lt-quiz-result__cta-media-stack">
          <img class="lt-quiz-result__cta-media-primary"
               src="{{ _cta_image }}" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          <img class="lt-quiz-result__cta-media-bonus"
               src="{{ _cta_image_bonus }}" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lt-quiz-result__cta-content">
      {%- comment -%} Primary: PDP-Klick als Haupt-CTA ───────────────── {%- endcomment -%}
      <p class="lt-quiz-result__cta-kicker">Dein nächster Schritt</p>
      <h3 class="lt-quiz-result__cta-text">
        Den AGE&amp;DNA-Test bestellen.
      </h3>
      <p class="lt-quiz-result__cta-sub">
        187 Reports zu 22 DNA-Bereichen plus dein epigenetisches Profil. Einmal testen, lebenslang nutzen.
      </p>
      <a
        class="lt-quiz-result__cta-primary"
        href="/products/lifetime-age-dna?utm_source=quiz&amp;utm_medium=result-page&amp;utm_campaign=cta-primary"
        data-result-pdp-cta
      >
        Zum AGE&amp;DNA-Test · 349&nbsp;€
      </a>

      {%- comment -%} Secondary: Guide + Rabatt per E-Mail ───────────── {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- comment -%} P3 — Guide/Rabatt demoted: eingeklappter Sekundär-Block statt gleichwertiger "Oder"-Option {%- endcomment -%}
      <details class="lt-quiz-result__guide">
        <summary class="lt-quiz-result__guide-summary">
          Noch nicht sicher? <strong>Longevity-101-Guide + 10&nbsp;% Rabatt</strong> per E-Mail sichern
        </summary>
        <div class="lt-quiz-result__guide-body">
      <form class="lt-quiz-result__form" data-result-form novalidate>
        <label class="lt-quiz-result__form-field">
          <span class="lt-quiz-result__form-label">E-Mail-Adresse</span>
          <input
            type="email"
            required
            placeholder="deine@email.de"
            class="lt-quiz-result__form-input"
            data-result-email
          >
        </label>
        <button type="submit" class="lt-quiz-result__form-submit">
          Guide + 10&nbsp;% Rabatt sichern
        </button>
        <p class="lt-quiz-result__form-error" data-result-error hidden role="alert"></p>
        <p class="lt-quiz-result__form-consent-note">
          Mit dem Absenden bestätigst du, den Guide und gelegentliche LIFETIME-Updates per E-Mail erhalten zu wollen. Abmeldung jederzeit möglich.
        </p>
      </form>

      <div class="lt-quiz-result__success" hidden data-result-success>
        <p class="lt-quiz-result__success-line">✓ Danke! Dein Longevity-Guide und 10 %-Rabattcode kommen gleich per E-Mail.</p>
      </div>
        </div>
      </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} P1 — Sticky Kauf-CTA (Mobile): immer erreichbar im langen Result-Scroll {%- endcomment -%}
  <a
    class="lt-quiz-result__sticky-cta"
    href="/products/lifetime-age-dna?utm_source=quiz&amp;utm_medium=result-page&amp;utm_campaign=cta-sticky"
    data-result-pdp-cta
    aria-label="Zum AGE und DNA-Test bestellen, 349 Euro"
  >
    <span class="lt-quiz-result__sticky-cta-label">Zum AGE&amp;DNA-Test</span>
    <span class="lt-quiz-result__sticky-cta-price">349&nbsp;€</span>
  </a>

</div>
